text SSTidalRooms_Text_TakeRestOnBed {
	"There's a bed…
	Let's take a rest."
}

text SSTidalRooms_Text_ColtonIntro {
	"I often sail to LILYCOVE CITY.

	I enjoy attending CONTESTS,
	you see."
}

text SSTidalRooms_Text_ColtonDefeat {
	"That was an enjoyable match!"
}

text SSTidalRooms_Text_ColtonPostBattle {
	"I get so excited imagining what kinds
	of POKéMON I'll get to see in the next
	CONTEST. The anticipation of it thrills!"
}

text SSTidalRooms_Text_MicahIntro {
	"Are your friends strong?"
}

text SSTidalRooms_Text_MicahDefeat {
	"Your friends are, indeed, strong."
}

text SSTidalRooms_Text_MicahPostBattle {
	"Friends need not be human.
	For me, POKéMON are treasured friends!"
}

text SSTidalRooms_Text_ThomasIntro {
	"Child…
	Did you knock on the door?"
}

text SSTidalRooms_Text_ThomasDefeat {
	"A loss is to be accepted without haste
	or panic."
}

text SSTidalRooms_Text_ThomasPostBattle {
	"To be never ruffled in any situation is
	the GENTLEMAN's code of conduct."
}

text SSTidalRooms_Text_JedIntro {
	"JED: I feel a little shy about this, but…
	We'll show you our lovey-dovey power!"
}

text SSTidalRooms_Text_JedDefeat {
	"JED: Sigh…"
}

text SSTidalRooms_Text_JedPostBattle {
	"JED: It's the first time that our lovey-
	dovey power couldn't prevail!
	You must be an awesome TRAINER!"
}

text SSTidalRooms_Text_JedNotEnoughMons {
	"JED: You only have one POKéMON?
	Isn't that just too lonesome?"
}

text SSTidalRooms_Text_LeaIntro {
	"LEA: I feel a little silly, but…
	We'll show you our lovey-dovey power!"
}

text SSTidalRooms_Text_LeaDefeat {
	"LEA: Oh, boo!"
}

text SSTidalRooms_Text_LeaPostBattle {
	"LEA: I can't believe it!
	Our lovey-dovey power failed…
	You must be an awesome TRAINER!"
}

text SSTidalRooms_Text_LeaNotEnoughMons {
	"LEA: I wanted to battle…
	But you don't even have two POKéMON…"
}

text SSTidalRooms_Text_GarretIntro {
	"Ah, you've come just in time.

	I'm bored, you see.
	You may entertain me."
}

text SSTidalRooms_Text_GarretDefeat {
	"…That will do."
}

text SSTidalRooms_Text_GarretPostBattle {
	"Perhaps I shall get Father to acquire
	a yacht for me.
	A yacht for me and POKéMON!"
}

text SSTidalRooms_Text_NaomiIntro {
	"Oh, you're such an adorable TRAINER.
	Would you like to have tea?
	Or would you rather battle?"
}

text SSTidalRooms_Text_NaomiDefeat {
	"I see.
	You're the active sort."
}

text SSTidalRooms_Text_NaomiPostBattle {
	"A world cruise on a luxury liner has its
	charms, I must say…

	But, I will admit there is an appealing
	side to touring HOENN by ferry."
}

text SSTidalRooms_Text_NotSuspiciousTakeThis {
	"Uh… Hi! I… I'm not acting suspicious!
	Uh… You can have this! For free!

	It… Honestly, I didn't SNATCH it from
	someone! I'd never do such a thing!
	It's clean! You can use it!"
}

text SSTidalRooms_Text_ExplainSnatch {
	"SNATCH steals the beneficial effects
	of certain moves before they can be
	used by a foe or ally."
}
